---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Market Notes — JSong Realty Blog | Atlanta Real Estate Insights"
  description="Atlanta real-estate market notes, neighborhood explainers, and buyer/seller playbooks from Joshua Song."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp; Blog</nav>
      <span class="eyebrow">Market Notes</span>
      <h1>Short, useful reads about <span class="serif-italic">Atlanta real estate.</span></h1>
      <p>Neighborhood deep-dives, market data, and buyer/seller playbooks — from the ground in the city I work every day.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="blog-grid">

        <article class="blog-card reveal">
          <a href="/blog/sample-post/" class="blog-thumb">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560518883-ce09059eeffa?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Atlanta skyline" loading="lazy" />
          </a>
          <span class="blog-meta">Market · April 2026 · 6 min read</span>
          <h3><a href="/blog/sample-post/">Atlanta's Intown Market in Q1 2026: Three Things That Actually Matter</a></h3>
          <p>Rates moved. Inventory shifted. Here's what the headlines got wrong — and what buyers and sellers should do about it.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="blog-card reveal delay-1">
          <a href="/blog/sample-post/" class="blog-thumb">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464146072230-91cabc968266?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Virginia-Highland street with trees" loading="lazy" />
          </a>
          <span class="blog-meta">Neighborhood · March 2026 · 8 min read</span>
          <h3><a href="/blog/sample-post/">The Honest Guide to Buying in Virginia-Highland</a></h3>
          <p>A street-by-street breakdown of what's actually worth the premium — and where the hidden value still sits.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="blog-card reveal delay-2">
          <a href="/blog/sample-post/" class="blog-thumb">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1450101499163-c8848c66ca85?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Contract documents on a desk" loading="lazy" />
          </a>
          <span class="blog-meta">Buyer's guide · March 2026 · 5 min read</span>
          <h3><a href="/blog/sample-post/">Escalation Clauses: When They Win Houses, and When They Don't</a></h3>
          <p>A misused escalation clause can leave $30k on the table. Here's how to structure one that actually works.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="blog-card reveal">
          <a href="/blog/sample-post/" class="blog-thumb">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556909114-f6e7ad7d3136?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Staged living room interior" loading="lazy" />
          </a>
          <span class="blog-meta">Seller's guide · February 2026 · 7 min read</span>
          <h3><a href="/blog/sample-post/">Staging ROI in Atlanta: What's Worth It, What's Theater</a></h3>
          <p>The three staging investments that actually show up in your sale price, and the ones that don't.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="blog-card reveal delay-1">
          <a href="/blog/sample-post/" class="blog-thumb">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1502005229762-cf1b2da7c5d6?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="BeltLine walking trail" loading="lazy" />
          </a>
          <span class="blog-meta">Neighborhood · February 2026 · 6 min read</span>
          <h3><a href="/blog/sample-post/">The BeltLine Westside: Where the Growth Actually Is</a></h3>
          <p>A data-backed look at which blocks are appreciating fastest — and why the obvious hot spots aren't always the best bets.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="blog-card reveal delay-2">
          <a href="/blog/sample-post/" class="blog-thumb">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503387762-592deb58ef4e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Modern new construction home" loading="lazy" />
          </a>
          <span class="blog-meta">Buyer's guide · January 2026 · 4 min read</span>
          <h3><a href="/blog/sample-post/">New Construction in Atlanta: Read the Contract First</a></h3>
          <p>Builder contracts favor the builder. Here are the seven clauses I always push back on — and what I ask for in return.</p>
        </article>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-muted">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-band reveal">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-light">Newsletter</span>
          <h2>Want these in your inbox?</h2>
          <p>Monthly Atlanta market notes. No spam, no upsells, easy unsubscribe.</p>
        </div>
        <a class="btn btn-accent btn-lg" href="/contact/">Subscribe</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
